D E _ S A U N A K A T A R I I N A

By NakkiMaisteri


MAP BRIEFING

After a horrible murder at women locker room a taliban ghost started to haunt the place. The whole building had to be shutten down. The local terrorist "gang" heard about this incident they decided to blow up the whole building. While they were making their assault a counter terrorist force just happened to be inspecting the area. Are you alone?

OBJECTIVE
Terrorists: Plant the bomb in one out of three "sauna", area on the map and destroy the building along with the ghost.
Counter terrorists: Protect the sauna from demolition by all cost!

MAP INFORMATION

Map contains: "Ability to run outside / Scary place / secret areas / ETC"
Recommented players/Max players: 20/40
Map contains three bomb site.
Spawnpoints: Terrorists spawn from trucks at both exits of the building. Counter terrorists spawn from locker room close to the bomb zones.
All of the map, isn't in the screenshots, EXPLORE!

Download --> Test --> Comment --> Rate.

Kittehs will thank you!
